# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your key, then restart `npm run dev`.
# `.env.local` is gitignored so your key never gets committed.
#
# Get a key at https://console.cloud.google.com:
#   1. Create/select a project
#   2. Enable "Maps JavaScript API" and "Geocoding API"
#   3. APIs & Services -> Credentials -> Create credentials -> API key
#
# Without this key the app still runs; the map screen shows a setup fallback
# and listing/request locations simply aren't geocoded.

VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
